file.name: ExternalDocumentationResource.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /{petId}:
    get:
      summary: Find pet by ID
      description: Returns a pet when 0 < ID <= 10.  ID > 10 or non integers will
        simulate API error conditions
      externalDocs:
        description: External Annotation Documentation
        url: http://url.me
      operationId: petId
      parameters:
      - name: petId
        in: path
        description: ID of pet that needs to be fetched
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int64
      responses:
        default:
          description: default response
          content:
            '*/*': {}

Error: notImplemented: path "/{petId}": get: responses: default: contents: unsupported content types: [*/*]
